<MethodEndpoint
  method={"delete"}
  path={"/api/v1.0/views/users/{viewUserId}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Deletes a user share assignment so the individual no longer has access to the view.

**Prerequisites**
1. **viewUserId** - Use [GET /api/v1.0/views/\{viewId\}/users](/docs/api/views/list-view-users) to list shares and extract `Items[].ViewUserId`.

**Workflow Example**
1. List user shares: [GET /api/v1.0/views/\{viewId\}/users](/docs/api/views/list-view-users).
2. Delete the share: [DELETE /api/v1.0/views/users/\{viewUserId\}](/docs/api/views/delete-view-user).

**Minimal Required Fields**: `viewUserId` (path).
